AVERMEDIA INFO said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 6.84% to NT$216,963,000 from NT$232,888,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            216,963          232,888    
YOY%              -6.84%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            969,218         1,621,286   
YOY%             -40.22% 
=================================================================
 